the stadium\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"the roads\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The support was overwhelming.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The support\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe my life has changed because of this and I have also changed a lot of lives in my home country.\\\"\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"lives\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"my home country\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having now returned to Europe, Tebogo will go head-to-head with American Fred Kerley over 200m at Thursday's Diamond League meeting in Lausanne.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998089479632905, \"rank\": 0.0001661618920907167, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}, {\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.7787193942909765, \"rank\": 0.28415956351103616, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"score\": 0.9999987028131045, \"rank\": 1.2971882482863886e-06, \"text\": \"Lausanne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"200m\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The road ahead, he said, involved bringing the 100m and the 400m more into his crosshairs.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The road\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"his crosshairs\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have talked it through with my coach about the possibility of competing in the 400m,\\\" he said, having also been part of Botswana's 4x400m relay squad that won a thrilling silver in Paris.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.527156061905672e-13, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999971403213, \"rank\": 2.8597839678116705e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"a thrilling silver\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The plan is to focus on the 100 and 200m first.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The plan\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning gold in both, we will then consider switching to the 400m.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since I have already won the 200m gold, now the 100m is the main goal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 200m gold\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"the main goal\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While South African Reggie Walker won the 100m gold at the 1908 London Games, it has not been repeated in modern history.\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"South African Reggie Walker\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m gold\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1908 London Games\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"modern history\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closest an African sprinter has come was Frankie Fredericks, the Namibian winning two 100m silvers (along with two 200m silvers) at both the 1992 and 1996 Games.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frankie_Fredericks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frankie Fredericks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frankie_Fredericks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frankie_Fredericks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an African sprinter\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"the Namibian\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"two 100m silvers\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"two 200m silvers\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"both the 1992 and 1996 Games\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see that as a disadvantage,\\\" Tebogo said of no African winning it in recent times.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disadvantage\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"recent times\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Instead, it's more of an encouragement to make history.\\\"\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an encouragement\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His 200m gold in Paris had been a boon \\\"not just for my country, but also for the entire African continent\\\", Tebogo argued.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999971403213, \"rank\": 2.8597839678116705e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His 200m gold\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"a boon\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire African continent\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have shown that against all odds, everything is possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all odds\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"What happens next in my life as an athlete is about continuing to push those boundaries and inspire more people to believe in their potential.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"those boundaries\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"more people\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"their potential\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The journey has just begun and I am excited for what the future holds.\\\"\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The journey\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo received two houses from the government as a reward for his gold medal showing, but he insisted he would stay put at the home of his late mother Seratiwa's for the time being.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"two houses\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"a reward\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"his gold medal\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"the home\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"his late mother\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"Seratiwa\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His mother, who travelled to many of the meets and championships he raced in, died suddenly in May whilst Tebogo was away in the United States.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2912, \"end\": 2925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8594169233530746, \"rank\": 0.1635169809481742, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http: